# 🧠 Important design decision

## Why cookie is better than query param

### ❌ Bad

```text
https://b2boost...?sessionId=abc123
```

* visible in URL
* insecure
* leaks in logs

---

### ✅ Good

```http
Set-Cookie: SESSION_ID=abc123
```

* HttpOnly → JS can’t read it
* Secure → HTTPS only (prod)
* cleaner

